The aging profile of the Portuguese population: a principal component analysis.

Rodrigues V(1), Mota-Pinto A, de Sousa B, Botelho A, Alves C, de Oliveira CR.

Author information:
(1)Instituto de Higiene e Medicina Social, Faculdade de Medicina da, 
Universidade de Coimbra, Rua Larga, 3004-504, Coimbra, Portugal, 
