surgery and blood pressure normalised in 86.4 % of those who had had 
hypertension preoperatively. Obstructive sleep apnoea and obesity 
hypoventilation syndrome also improved significantly in 92 % of the patients.
CONCLUSIONS: Morbidly obese patients can undergo biliodigestive surgery safely 
